<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>Kenyan Counties API</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">

    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon.png" />

    <meta content="Kenyan Counties API" property="og:title">
    <meta content="Get list of counties from kenya and their information via RESTful API" name="description">
    <meta name="keywords" content="rest,api,counties,countie,kenya,json">
    <meta name="author" content="Yusuf Hamisi">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/uikit@3.6.22/dist/css/uikit.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/prismjs@1.23.0/themes/prism.css">

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/uikit@3.6.22/dist/js/uikit.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/uikit@3.6.22/dist/js/uikit-icons.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/prismjs@1.23.0/components/prism-core.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/prismjs@1.23.0/plugins/autoloader/prism-autoloader.min.js"></script>
  </head>

  <body>
    <header style="border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa;">
      <nav class="uk-navbar-container" uk-navbar>
        <div class="uk-navbar-left">
          <div class="uk-navbar-item">
            <span class="uk-text-bold uk-text-large">Counties API</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="uk-navbar-right">
          <ul class="uk-navbar-nav">
            <li>
              <a href="https://github.com/yusuf-khamis/counties" target="_blank" rel="noreferer,noopener">
                <span uk-icon="github"></span>
                <span class="uk-text-capitalize uk-margin-small-left">Github</span>
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="uk-flex uk-flex-center">
      <div class="uk-width-3-4@l uk-width-5-6@s  uk-padding uk-background-muted">
        <p class="uk-text-large">Counties API</h1>
        <p>Get list of Kenyan counties and their information</p>
        <p>Current version: {{ version }}</p>

        <hr class="uk-margin-medium">

        <p class="uk-text-large">API Endpoints</p>
        <p>Below are described the REST endpoints available that you can use to search for counties</p>

        <hr class="uk-margin-medium">

        <p class="uk-text-large">All</p>
        <pre><code class="language-uri">https://counties-kenya.herokuapp.com/api/v1</code></pre>

        <hr class="uk-margin-medium">

        <p class="uk-text-large">Name</p>
        <p>Search by county name</p>
        <pre><code class="language-uri">https://counties-kenya.herokuapp.com/api/v1/name/{name}
https://counties-kenya.herokuapp.com/api/v1/name/nairobi

// The name of the county should be in lowercase, and if two words are involved, separate using hyphen
https://counties-kenya.herokuapp.com/api/v1/name/homa-bay</code></pre>

        <hr class="uk-margin-medium">

        <p class="uk-text-large">Capital</p>
        <p>Search by county capital</p>
        <pre><code class="language-uri">https://counties-kenya.herokuapp.com/api/v1/capital/{name}
https://counties-kenya.herokuapp.com/api/v1/capital/bomet

// The name of the capital of the county should be in lowercase, and if two words are involved, separate using hyphen
https://counties-kenya.herokuapp.com/api/v1/capital/ol-kalou</code></pre>

        <hr class="uk-margin-medium">

        <p class="uk-text-large">Code</p>
        <p>Search by county code</p>
        <pre><code class="language-uri">https://counties-kenya.herokuapp.com/api/v1/code/{code}
https://counties-kenya.herokuapp.com/api/v1/code/23</code></pre>

        <hr class="uk-margin-medium">
        
        <p class="uk-text-large">Sort</p>
        <p>
          Sort response by either
          <span class="uk-text-italic uk-text-bold">name</span>,
          <span class="uk-text-italic uk-text-bold">code</span> or
          <span class="uk-text-italic uk-text-bold">areaSqKm</span>
          both directions
        </p>
        <pre><code class="language-uri">https://counties-kenya.herokuapp.com/api/v1?order={field}
https://counties-kenya.herokuapp.com/api/v1?order=name
https://counties-kenya.herokuapp.com/api/v1?order=code
https://counties-kenya.herokuapp.com/api/v1?order=areaSqKm

// Response is sorted in ascending order by default, to sort in descending order add 'dir=desc'
https://counties-kenya.herokuapp.com/api/v1?order=name&amp;dir=desc</code></pre>
        
        <hr class="uk-margin-medium">
        
        <p class="uk-text-large">Response Example</p>
        <pre><code class="language-json">[
  {
    "name": "Nandi",
    "code": "29",
    "areaSqKm": "2884.5", // area in square kilometres
    "capital": [
      "Kapsabet"
    ]
  }
]</code></pre>

        <hr class="uk-margin-medium">

        <p class="uk-text-large">Filter Response</p>
        <p>You can filter the output of your request to include only the specified fields</p>
        <pre><code class="language-uri">https://counties-kenya.herokuapp.com/api/v1?fields={...fields}
https://counties-kenya.herokuapp.com/api/v1?fields=name,code</code></pre>

        <hr class="uk-margin-medium">

        <p class="uk-text-large">Source</p>
        <p>
          <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Counties_of_Kenya" class="uk-link" target="_blank" rel="noreferer,noopener">Wikipedia</a>
        </p>

        <hr class="uk-margin-medium">

        <p class="uk-text-large">License</p>
        <p>
          <a href="https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/MPL/2.0/" class="uk-link" target="_blank" rel="noreferer,noopener">Mozilla Public License (MPL 2.0)</a>
        </p>
        <p class="uk-text-muted">Made with â™¥ by Yusuf Hamisi (yusufkhamis27@gmail.com)</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>